{"word":"H1342 - גָּאָה - gâʼâh - gaw-aw' - Gloriously","slug":"H1342","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּאָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gâʼâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gloriously"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D0;&#x05D4; - ga&#x0302;'a&#x0302;h</b> - <i>gaw-aw'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>mount</i> up; hence in general to <i>rise</i>, (figuratively) be <i>majestic: - </i>gloriously, grow up, increase, be risen, triumph."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1341\">H1341</a>, <a href=\"#/H1343\">H1343</a>, <a href=\"#/H1344\">H1344</a>, <a href=\"#/H1345\">H1345</a>, <a href=\"#/H1346\">H1346</a>, <a href=\"#/H1347\">H1347</a>, <a href=\"#/H1348\">H1348</a>, <a href=\"#/H1349\">H1349</a>, <a href=\"#/H1466\">H1466</a>"}]}